#3601
A Marble Dome~
   A large circular area with a domed ceiling.  Everything is constructed from
sleek black marble slabs.  The main focal point of the room is a vast mural
painted on the dome shaped ceiling.  &RPlease notice the tablet at the center
of the room&n, which will explain what lies to the north, east, and west.  To
go back to the Temple of Kir Drax'in head down the stairs.  
~
