#3602
Memorial to the Fallen~
   The graveyard grass is primly manicured into a pleasant knoll to rest upon.
Stone benches made from the same rock as the gravestones surround a large,
expressively carved fountain.  The gentle trickle of water makes this a
soothing place to rest and reflect on the lessons learned from fallen heroes.
~
