Among Toppled Gravestones~
   The grass is trampled and there appears to be smears of blood amidst the
blades.  Once pristine gravestones lie toppled on their sides in a bold
display of desecration.  The smell of urine is strong indicating the presence
of someone or something that has little regard for honoring the dead.  
~
