#3605
Beside a Desiccated Crypt~
   The crumbling, carved stone edifice centered in this room is an unfortunate
victim to time itself.  This crypt whomever it was dedicated to was of great
nobility to Kir'Draxin but the who and the when have been eroded by the
omnipresent forces of time iteself.  There are numerous holes broken into the
sides of the crypt probably by thieves in time long forgotten.  
~
