A Ring of Flowers~
   A circle of white peace lilys marks a place of solemn reflection upon the
lost.  A cool breeze rustles the leaves of tall dogwood trees at the peak of
their bloom.  Though there appears to be much foot traffic through here,
visitors have taken great care not to trample the flowers.  
