Beneath A Weeping Willow~
   Lush, parabolic branches hide this spot from the blazing sun.  True to its
name, the faint echoes of mourning seem to emanate from the crown of a large
weeping willow.  The soft trickling of a large, ornately carved fountain echoes
about.  
