#3609
Behind A Gardener's Shed~
   Standing behind a small shed, little remains but the frame and a few
splintered planks hanging by a handful of nails.  The chaotic scene looks as
if the shed was dismantled from the outside by a predator desperate to catch
its prey inside.  The dirt is scuffed and dried blood splatters the wood like
a shoddy paint job.  Shuffling sounds of debris indicate the presence of
something or someone among the clutter.  
~
