#3610
At the Nameless Guardian~
   A large, iron statue depicts a nameless warrior standing guard.  It looms
stoically, in honor of all fallen protectors who gave their lives without
fanfare to protect the innocent.  The energy and will of the righteous dead
gathers into the statue and emits an aura of tranquility over this monument.

