#3612
A Holy Mausoleum~
   A large square structure stands alone in the field.  It is ornately carved
from a single block of marble with black and gold innervations.  The
decoration and inscriptions pay homage to a revered holy man who lived a life
of faithful service to his god.  At the apex of the structure is a holy
symbol, a blazing phoenix, looking down with watchful eyes on all who come to
pay respects.  
