#3617
The Dead Oaks~
   A copse of large oak trees casts shade all around.  The trees appear hollow
and lifeless, bare of any leaves with peeling bark that exposes the rot
beneath.  Something sinister has drained the life force of everything within
reach of the trees as this dead spot conspicuously stands out among the rest
of the graveyard.  There appears to be a hill leading up from this wretched
place.  
~
