#3618
An Overlook~
   Nestled atop this small hill is a comfortable collection of benches.  
Arranged strategically, the seats offer a peaceful view of the graveyard all
around.  Silhouettes of humanoids can be seen milling about in search of loved
ones.  But more disturbingly are the outlines of beasts and other dangerous
looking creatures patiently stalking the visitors.  
