#3620
A Bed of Daisies~
   An abundance of white daisies gives this spot the look of a soft bank of
snow.  However, the scent is undeniably floral in nature as the sweet notes
dance in the light breeze.  There are matted spots marking the places previous
passersby sat to rest their weary feet.  Birds dart in and out, chasing the
abundance of insects feeding off the sweet nectar hidden beneath the petals.

