#3621
A Rotting Chapel~
   A small, decayed chapel stands precariously on an unsteady foundation.  
The peeling paint leaves the exterior blotched like a beggar with leprosy.  
The paneless windows reveal rotted pews occupied by skeletons dressed in their
best clothes.  The lightning might be playing tricks but it seems as if the
skeletal figures are not exactly still.  
~
