#3622
A Grove of Dogwoods~
   A tiny grove of dogwood trees encircles a small, decorative fountain.  
The tall trees in bloom with small white flowers, speckled with red, provides
a cheerful place to rest among the dead.  Looking across the grove, small
mammals can be seen running between the trees looking for places to hide.  
The grounds are relatively clean except for a handful of empty waterskins
indicative of previous visitors utilizing the grove.  
~
