A Monument to Nature~
   A large wooden effigy stands alone in this field.  It was painstakingly
carved by artisans to honor the fallen protectors of nature.  A bright
painting on the face of the effigy depicts a stoic ranger facing a shadowy
figure threatening his domain.  The effigy appears to be constructed of
polished ebony planks adorned in live garland with subtle thorns hiding behind
the leaves.  
