#3627
A Regal Tomb~
   Before a large tomb, various decorations depict an organized and
well-stocked military depot.  Dedicated to a famous quartermaster renown for
his martial prowess and later his ability to keep an army outfitted, this
burial site is a wonder to behold.  The carvings detail every campaign the
quartermaster marched, from his days as frontline fodder to his final duty of
supplying the Kir Drax'in army with equipment to defend the vast city from
invasion.  
