particular spot, a number of benches are arranged in a concentric circle,
surrounding a large, ornate fountain.  The benches are carved from a brilliant
and deep brown hardwood, clear lacquered and polished to an exquisite shine.
The water of the fountain is crystal clear and looks incredibly refreshing.  
