A Towering Memorial~
   A quiet little garden marks the entrance to a tall building made from faded
red brick.  Banners of the Kir Drax'in guard regiment line the walkway leading
up to a tall, silver double-gated entry.  Emblems carved into the walkway mark
this memorial as being dedicated to the fallen leaders of the Kir Drax'in
guard.  Beyond the silver gates are a steep set of stairs leading up.  
