A Plain, Well-kept Room~
   The first floor of the building is rather ordinary with little detail
standing out.  Paintings line the walls showing Kir Drax'in in various stages
of historical development.  Starting on the left, the groundbreaking ceremony
for the city hall is attended by only a handful of modestly dressed people.  
The painting to the right is almost identical to the modern day city as it
currently exists.  
