#3638
The Officers' Lounge~
   This larger break area is designed to honor the high officers.  The decor
is much fancier with marble flooring and designer drapes.  The bar is large
and made of a bright mahogany shined up to perfection.  High-backed chairs
upholstered in rich, colorful leathers scatter about the floor, separated by
beautiful oak tables for two.  A door in the back of the room reveals stairs
leading up.  
