#3639
The Officers' Quarters~
   This office contains several large, cherrywood desks each with a small
portait atop.  Examining the portraits, the famous lieutenants from various
stories and ballads are honored with life-like illustrations sitting among
their various medals and commendations.  One particularly large desk has a
portrait that stands out from the rest with a faded caption referencing
Danziq.  The surface of the larger desk is completely obscured with piles of
medals and awards far more ornate and colorful than the rest, the desk of a
hero.  
