#3641
The Captain's Office~
   This office is no fancier than the rest of the memorial but is kept much
neater.  The arrangement of furniture draws the eye to a large portrait on the
back wall of a huge, grizzled man in a crisp, highly decorated uniform.  
Along the walls flanking the portrait hang various trophies ranging from
commissioned medals to wicked-looking skulls.  No doubt this office was built
to honor the most famous and effective captain of the guard from the wild and
storied history of Kir Drax'in.  
~
