#3689
The Cemetery Entrance~
   Peeking through the gates, a wide field of gravestones amd mausoleums dot
the landscape.  Flickers of movement catch the eye along the paths weaving
through the graves of fallen Kir Drax'in heroes.  A worn path is beaten into
the grass and weeds from the shuffling feet of visitors come to pay respects.
There is a towering black stone &W&Wtablet&n towering over you near the gates.  
~
