#3691
Dark Pawns' Newbie Emporium~
   The air in this room smells heavily of leather, dyes, and oil.  Light is
cast from a large lantern burning brightly that illuminates the vast array of
supplies lining the walls.  Each dark oak shelf has been neatly organized and
not a speck of dust could be found on any surface.  A large counter spans the
far eastern wall that provides a barrier to the more expensive items behind.
Neat stacks of paper sit on the surface of the desk.  
~
